    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Ensure that you have a convenient tool on you at all times with the ASR Outdoor Mini Key Chain Knife! This folding knife is just 2&quot; in length while folded, and extends to 2.75&quot; overall when unfolded making it an ideal size to keep in your pocket, on a key chain or in a travel bag. It&#039;s constructed of durable stainless steel, and the blade features the popular sheepsfoot style for cutting and slicing without needing a point. The pocket knife comes with a metal key chain that you can easily add to a belt loop, key ring or bag, and the blade handle features a cool red design. This is a must-have pocket tool for campers, hikers, travelers and anyone who can use a nifty blade while on the go!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Mini Folding Key Chain Knife 2.75 Inch Pocket Blade Tool</h2>\n  <p>Ensure that you have a convenient tool on you at all times with the ASR Outdoor Mini Key Chain Knife!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Made of 3CR13 Stainless Steel - Wont Rust (Designed in USA, Crafted in China)</li>\n    <li>SHEEPSFOOT BLADE - Blade Style Designed for Cutting &amp; Slicing Without Sharp Point - Great for Pockets</li>\n    <li>SMALL &amp; CONVENIENT SIZE - 2&quot; Folded | 2.75&quot; Overall Unfolded - Easy to Carry When Not in Use</li>\n    <li>KEY CHAIN FUNCTION - Comes with Adjustable Metal Key Chain - Easily Attach to Belt Loop, Key Ring, Bags etc.</li>\n    <li>COOL DESIGN - Blade Handle Features Shiny Red Finish for Unique Look</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/tools/folding_knives/HWT235RD_kychnknife_RD_main1.jpg\" alt=\"Ensure that you have a convenient tool on you at all times with the ASR Outdoor Mini Key Chain Knife\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASROFKCKRD</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886493921</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> 2.75 in</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This folding knife is just 2&quot; in length while folded, and extends to 2.75&quot; overall when unfolded making it an ideal size to keep in your pocket, on a key chain or in a travel bag. It&#039;s constructed of durable stainless steel, and the blade features the popular sheepsfoot style for cutting and slicing without needing a point.</p>\n  <p>The pocket knife comes with a metal key chain that you can easily add to a belt loop, key ring or bag, and the blade handle features a cool red design. This is a must-have pocket tool for campers, hikers, travelers and anyone who can use a nifty blade while on the go!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
